Re-selling MC Goods

Matthias Fuchs

October 3rd, 2019

Data description

Color and Asking Price

Looking at color popularity by the year of first registration and by model

I was inspired to run this analysis after reading this articel: https://www.whatcar.com/news/what-are-the-best-car-colours-for-resale-value/n18356. It actually works a lot better. Apparently specific color suit individiual car models from specific years better others. Whoever designs a car like this, benefits from a value gain.

Average holding duration of cars is 5.6 years in Germany (Focus Online, 2012) and around 8.68 years for new cars (DAT Report, 2016)
